= Data Types

[cols="1,3,5a"]
|===
|Type |Description |Example

|`date` | https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601[ISO 8601] formatted string. | 1990-10-13
|`datetime` | https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601[ISO 8601] formatted string. | 2016-03-11T03:45:40+00:00

|`image`
|To set: a base64 encoded string.

When read: a hash with keys that are urls to various sizes of the image.  Every image will at least have
a `full_size` key which is the image in the same resolution as it was uploaded.
| When read:

++++
<%= json \
    full_size: 'https://example.com/image.png'
%>
++++

|===

